des: Oi, clean shirt! This skill lets you get quotes from your favourite Peep Show characters. Start with Mark or Jez - just tell Alexa who you want to hear from. If you're a bit of a Peep Show legend, there's also the premium version, which is what you need to get quotes from loads more characters (we're talking Super Hans, Dobby, Gerard, Johnson, Gog, Elena, Jeff, The Orgazoid and more...). Just say Alexa, open Peep Show Quotes to get started!
